com.percussion.services.filter
Interface IPSItemFilterRuleDef

All Superinterfaces:
Comparable
public interface IPSItemFilterRuleDef
extends Comparable

A rule def associates a specific filter rule (stored by the extensions manager) with a set of parameters to be used with it. Rules are used to remove items that do not meet one or more criteria, and to adjust what revisions of items are used.

Author:
dougrand
See Also:
